  "texts": [
    "GANs are made up of a generator and a discriminator [210].",
    "The aim of the generator is to create the fake samples that are similar to the training samples to deceive the discriminator.",
    "In contrast, the discriminator focuses on distinguishing the real and fake samples.",
    "During the training period, the adversarial relationship between the generator and discriminator enables them to improve the performance, until reaching a Nash equilibrium, where the discriminator cannot distinguish the real and fake samples.",
    "• Normalizing flows (NFs)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "GANs are made up of a generator and a discriminator [210]."
  ]
}